---
import Btn from '../Btn.astro'
import FakeLogs from '../FakeLogs.astro'
---

<div
  class="col-span-10 col-start-2 row-start-1 mt-12 flex flex-col md:col-span-6 md:col-start-2 md:row-start-1 md:mt-0"
>
  <FakeLogs />
</div>

<div
  class="col-span-10 col-start-2 row-span-3 row-start-1 mb-32 flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center pb-[10vh] md:pb-0"
>
  <h2 class="mb-12 text-center text-base font-black tracking-button text-white">
    I'M A<br />FRONT-END WEB DEVELOPER
  </h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col max-w-2xl ml-[8vw]">
    <div class="flex justify-between gap-12">
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Interdum rutrum fermentum
        ultrices dictum nisi etiam morbi tincidunt. Massa risus at sapien
        tristique leo egestas Fermentum ut nulla curabitur odio nisl malesuada
        fermentum. Amet eget diam elementum tellus nisi quisque nisl suspendisse
        at. Massa risus at sapien tristique leo egestas Fermentum ut nulla
        curabitur odio nisl malesuada fermentum.
      </p>

      <table class="max-w-xs text-xs">
        <tbody>
          <tr class="grid grid-cols-[5rem_1fr] gap-1">
            <th class="pl-0 pr-3 text-left text-primary-darker">SERVICES:</th>
            <td class="text-left">DEVELOPMENT && DESIGN</td>
            <th class="pl-0 pr-3 text-left text-primary-darker">COMPANY:</th>
            <td class="text-left">YOURS, MAYBE?</td>
            <th class="pl-0 pr-3 text-left text-primary-darker">MAIN TECH:</th>
            <td class="text-left"
              >TYPESCRIPT, REACT, NEXTJS, REACT-NATIVE, THREEJS, TAILWIND, SCSS</td
            >
            <th class="pl-0 pr-3 text-left text-primary-darker">TECH USED:</th>
            <td class="min-w-32 text-left">
              GRAPHQL + APOLLO + POTHOS, C/C++, ANDROID NDK, KOTLIN, PYTHON,
              BASH, DOCKER, HANDLEBARS, EXPRESSJS
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mt-[8vh] flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between pr-28"
    >
      <Btn href="/home" class="h-[4.5rem] w-52" frame>OK</Btn>
      <Btn href="/home" class="h-[4.5rem] w-52" frame>WHO ARE YOU?</Btn>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  p {
    @apply min-w-64 max-w-xs text-xs text-white opacity-80;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
</style>
